.DT
query_player_quest_info
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_player_quest_info

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_player_quest_info -  This method returns the quest info for a specific quest.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
mixed * query_player_quest_info(string pl_name,
string qu_info)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^pl_name%^RESET%^ - the player name
%^BOLD%^qu_info%^RESET%^ - the quest name
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the information associated with the quest

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/library.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the quest info for a specific quest.
This information is used for quests which have several parts to them
and information needs to be stored about the player as they attempt
to complete it.
.EP

